channel.title: Command Error
channel.description:
[code][client-1-Test]: Loading Process Completed [Has powers, lag: 6 ms] Exception encountered while parsing incoming packets from Test. java.lang.StringIndexOutOfBoundsException: String index out of range: -6 at java.lang.String.substring(String.java:1938) at java.lang.String.substring(String.java:1905) at client.customCommand(client.java:8262) at client.parseIncomingPackets(client.java:15291) at client.packetProcess(client.java:17032) at PlayerHandler.process(PlayerHandler.java:271) at process.run(process.java:23) at java.lang.Thread.run(Thread.java:619) ClientHandler: Client Test disconnected (127.0.0.1) Connection from 127.0.0.1:56550 [client-1-Test]: Loading Process Completed [Has powers, lag: 8 ms][/code] This comes up when any command is entered.
